lead_paragraph: South Africa’s rugby coach Allister Coetzee hailed the impact of Eddie Jones and the performance of England this year as the Springboks began their preparations for a four-match tour of Europe next month that includes a test at Twickenham.

headline.print_headline: Springbok Coach Hails England Side Ahead of Twickenham Test
